trait mcp.protocol {
  uses json.rpc.2.0
  uses stdio.transport
  protocol is ai.agent.interface
  protocol emits tool.results
  protocol emits resource.data
}

exegesis {
  The MCP protocol trait implements Model Context Protocol for AI agent integration
  via server.rs. JSON-RPC 2.0 methods: (1) initialize/initialized for handshake with
  protocol version "2024-11-05", (2) tools/list returns tool schemas with JSON
  Schema input definitions, (3) tools/call executes tools and returns structured
  results, (4) resources/list exposes URIs like orchestrator:
  resources/read fetches resource data by URI. Stdio transport reads newline-
  delimited JSON from stdin and writes responses to stdout, enabling Claude Code
  integration. OrchestratorMcpServer wraps StateStore, ClusterManager, Scheduler
  in Arc<RwLock<T>> for concurrent access.
}
